    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a showroom-quality specimen. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the body panels are perfectly straight with no dings, scratches, or imperfections. Inside, the cabin looks and smells like new, with the leather upholstery and trim showing zero signs of wear. Mechanically, it is in peak performance, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled garage. This is a rare find for a collector or an enthusiast who demands the very best.",
