      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The exterior has several noticeable scuffs, a few small dings, and the clear coat is beginning to thin in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery shows moderate wear and some staining, but the cabin remains functional. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, though it will likely need routine maintenance items like new tires and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid, honest car for someone looking for transportation at a reasonable price point.",
      "price": 20000.0,
