    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been clearly well-cared for, offering a dependable and smooth ride that you'll love. It\u2019s a wonderful, reliable choice for anyone looking for a solid car that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventure!",
